Q: Ifly S.A.航司的官网链接是什么？
SQL: SELECT supplier_website FROM supplier_details WHERE supplier_name = "Ifly S.A.";
actual_SQL:
SELECT supplier_website
FROM supplier_details
WHERE supplier_name = 'Ifly S.A.'
LIMIT 50;

Q: Alpha Aviation S.R.O.航司的官网链接是什么？
SQL: SELECT supplier_website FROM supplier_details WHERE supplier_name = "Alpha Aviation S.R.O.";
actual_SQL:
SELECT supplier_name,
       supplier_website
FROM supplier_details
WHERE supplier_name IN ('Alpha Aviation S.R.O.',
                        'Alpha Three Aviation')
LIMIT 50;
